{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act36side", "eventName": "泰拉飯", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DT-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "雨林解毒燉湯", "storyInfo": "小隊幾人原本想要找部落的智者大祭司求助，卻沒想到，被新世界的種種訊息塞滿了腦袋、正頭腦發昏的瑪露希爾不慎吃下了毒果，部落因此陷入了混亂。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungle_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊歐斯，快點跟上了啦。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快來看這顆蘑菇！迷宮裡最大的走路菇都沒有這麼大吧！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是走路菇長得這麼大該有多威風啊……等一下的午飯可以考慮吃它嗎？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你小心一點啊，美食指南裡說叢林裡面的蘑菇多多少少都有一些毒性。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如吃了之後會全身起疹子，會導致血液凝固，會不斷嘔吐直到把內臟都吐出來之類的……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不敢想像寫下這本指南的人都經歷了什麼。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫只跟著獸人學了分辨迷宮蘑菇的方法，這些沒見過的還是不要輕易嘗試了。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是這邊有動物把這種厚厚的蘑菇當作食物！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，如果只有一兩種動物在吃，那麼這種植物對大部分動物可能都有毒性。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換句話說，如果很多動物都在吃，那麼它才有可能是沒有毒性的。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#13$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低沉的咆哮）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼聲音？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#8$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（尖銳的蜂鳴）", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼東西往這邊飛來了！大家小心！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#11$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！", "name": "萊歐斯小隊"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$grenade_explosion", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.7, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength":